      <h3>1.2 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
      <p>We automatically collect certain information when you use our Service:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>IP address and device information</li>
        <li>Browser type and version</li>
        <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
        <li>Session duration and activity</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="use"><span class="section-number">2</span> How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use your information to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Provide the Service:</strong> Create accounts, process applications, facilitate matching</li>
        <li><strong>AI Recommendations:</strong> Analyze your profile to match you with suitable scholarships</li>
        <li><strong>Communication:</strong> Send notifications about applications, deadlines, and updates</li>
        <li><strong>Improvement:</strong> Analyze usage patterns to improve the Service</li>
        <li><strong>Security:</strong> Detect and prevent fraud, abuse, and security threats</li>
        <li><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> Comply with applicable laws and regulations</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="highlight-box info">
        <p><strong>AI Processing:</strong> Our AI recommendation system analyzes your academic profile, skills, and preferences to suggest scholarships. This analysis is performed automatically but does not make final decisions about your scholarship eligibility.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 id="share"><span class="section-number">3</span> Information Sharing</h2>
      <p>We share your information only in these situations:</p>

      <h3>3.1 With Scholarship Sponsors</h3>
      <p>When you apply for a scholarship, sponsors receive:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your name and contact information</li>
        <li>Academic information (GPA, course, year level)</li>
        <li>Uploaded documents</li>
        <li>Application letter and supporting materials</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>3.2 Service Providers</h3>
      <p>We use trusted third-party services for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Cloud hosting (Firebase/Google Cloud)</li>
        <li>Email delivery</li>
        <li>AI processing (OpenAI)</li>
        <li>Analytics</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>3.3 Legal Requirements</h3>
      <p>We may disclose information if required by law or to protect rights, safety, or property.</p>

      <h2 id="security"><span class="section-number">4</span> Data Security</h2>
      <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data:</p>

